{"tid":1468490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好將所有武力升級屈落鬼度","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:12:52.000Z","uid":3911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2750429bd24f29c4e939a255339ba70a64cfe682","tid":1468490,"uid":3911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"呢幾日一發現有鬼之後，就勁多人想將之前啲武力升級屈哂落佢哋度，我個人覺得係完全<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不可取</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為你文宣屈落鬼度，係變相話比其他人聽得鬼先會用升級武力，令到和理非對升級武力反感<br />\n<br />\n近幾日已經見到和理非將汽油彈啊，衝立會屈係鬼做即刻爽哂<br />\n<br />\n而家屈落鬼度係爽啊，但最後盞搞到和理非一面倒唔同意所有嘅升級行動，然後運動變成和平靜坐，跟住失敗"},{"pid":"b74fc0f49f3d1a45db507608a3c6f6b087f22f8e","tid":1468490,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"公關基本術，要一單嘢無人講最好係搵更爆嘅搶輿論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQqX7f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQqX7f2.png&h=43c4a5fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71ccb44bb4fece308fb2c0617ec618b73f776af0","tid":1468490,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">試下用 我不會放棄機場 回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/024448_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F024448_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=e8db9d71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/024449_d328056414c9204c8e86b080c75810da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu